data.description:
Tucked into idyllic Atlantic Beach, Florida and three blocks from the ocean, Hotel Palms is a modern, beachside motor court hotel. Hotel Palms is a boutique hotel within walking distance to the shops and restaurants of Beaches Town Center, a beachside community in the heart of Atlantic and Neptune Beach. Reclaimed wood headboards, palm trees, concrete floors, and uncluttered design inspire visions of beach house living. 

A short drive to Jacksonville Beach, Hotel Palms is the only boutique hotel located in the Jacksonville Beach area. Ideal for intimate outdoor weddings, parties, and events, Hotel Palms is also located near the Mayport Naval Station and Mayo Clinic.

From the local beers served in The Lounge to the outdoor shower in the courtyard, the design, amenities and Hotel Palms experience have been carefully considered to make guests feel like locals all while enjoying a restful and relaxing stay.

Here are just a few things the Hotel Palms has to offer:

Beer and wine lounge
Private courtyard
Customizable Unlikely Local itineraries
Outdoor shower
Patio seating
Outdoor fireplace
Breakfast delivery
Complimentary wifi
Free beach cruiser and foam board rentals

From bike riding through the neighboring residential areas and eating at locally owned restaurants to day tripping to the nearby towns of historic St. Augustine and Fernandina Beach, the Hotel Palms knowledgeable and accommodating staff is always available to create customizable itineraries, known as the Unlikely Local℠ experience.So, pack your bag but travel lightly as our rooms, amenities, and location are all you’ll need to feel like a local, if just for a weekend.
